data.description: Welcome to this secluded oasis! Nestled on over an acre of lush land, this charming home boasts 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms, featuring an inviting open floor plan adorned with a spacious kitchen equipped with an island and gleaming stainless steel appliances. The first-floor master suite offers indulgence with its ensuite showcasing a luxurious large tub, dual sinks, a walk-in shower, and an expansive walk-in closet. Completing the downstairs are two generously sized bedrooms, while upstairs, a versatile finished flex space awaits, ideal for an office, playroom, or more. Additionally, an unfinished attic space provides endless possibilities. Step outside to discover a vast fenced backyard, offering ample space for outdoor activities, and don't forget to bring your chickens - this home comes complete with a ready-to-use chicken coop. Conveniently located not far from all that Moore County has to offer, this home effortlessly combines comfort and convenience for a truly exceptional living experience.
